## Why This Is Asked

This question evaluates the ability to design a small-scale iOS app with proper data persistence, SwiftUI architecture, and accessibility considerations. It tests understanding of Core Data relationships, SwiftUI patterns, data visualization, and inclusive design principles.

## Key Concepts

- Core Data modeling with relationships (Habit + Completion entities)
- SwiftUI MVVM architecture with @FetchRequest
- Data aggregation for heatmap visualization
- Accessibility implementation (VoiceOver, Dynamic Type)
- Core Data migration strategies and unit testing approaches

## Code Example

```swift
// Core Data model sketch
class Habit: NSManagedObject {
  @NSManaged var id: UUID
